00:31:10.304 --> 00:31:11.720
So the greatest
thing we can do is

00:31:11.720 --> 00:31:17.450
to actually notice all
of the person and to say,

00:31:17.450 --> 00:31:20.240
you know what you really seem
to care about is X, Y, and Z

00:31:20.240 --> 00:31:22.510
and be that.

00:31:22.510 --> 00:31:24.370
I like to say that
most of us can't

00:31:24.370 --> 00:31:28.220
