of hard because you're

00:31:32.930 --> 00:31:33.680
in the fuzz of it.

00:31:33.680 --> 00:31:36.440
You're literally like mashed
up against the glass of it.

00:31:36.440 --> 00:31:41.299
And so friends can say, this is
something that you care about.

00:31:41.299 --> 00:31:42.590
[? Obie ?] totally gets me too.

00:31:42.590 --> 00:31:44.700
So I'm waiting for her to tell
me my onlyness for a second.

00:31:44.700 --> 00:31:46.670
But it's like a light
bulb above your head.

00:31:46.670 --> 00:31:49.350
When you walk into a room,
the whole room changes.

00:31:49.350 --> 00:31:52.430
So if that light
bulb is tamarind

00:31:52.430 --> 00:31:56.390
orange versus neon orange, it's
a different thing in that room,

00:31:56.390 --> 00:31:58.370
or mallard blue, right?

00:31:58.370 --> 00:32:00.350
And so if your friends
can say to you,

00:32:00.350 --> 00:32:02.570
this seems to be this thing
you really care about,

00:32:02.570 --> 00:32:04.376
it helps reflect it back.

00:32:04.376 --> 00:32:05.750
And so maybe that's
the one thing

00:32:05.750 --> 00:32:09.050
