her history and experience

00:32:11.550 --> 00:32:13.670
as well as her visions
and hopes, even

00:32:13.670 --> 00:32:16.370
something that's just a
thread she's ultimately

00:32:16.370 --> 00:32:17.290
going to pull on.

00:32:17.290 --> 00:32:20.151
Does that help?

00:32:20.151 --> 00:32:20.650
Yeah?

